    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional character and proven reliability. This automobile has been maintained to a rigorous standard, ensuring that both its mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal remain distinctly superior. Featuring a refined interior and a drivetrain engineered for longevity, it offers a sophisticated driving experience. Each component has undergone a comprehensive professional evaluation to guarantee peak performance for its next proprietor. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that balances lasting value with uncompromising quality.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
